acceptance_criteria: "pm next (toon and json) no longer contains two full projections of the same item; the ready-list contract (excludes recommended, or id-ref) is documented in command docs and SDK contracts; contract snapshot tests assert non-duplication; MCP pm_next envelope matches"
parent: pm-mpbb
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: Removed the recommended row from the ready tail while preserving evaluation and ranking semantics.
expected_result: "pm next emits one canonical recommended object without duplicating it as ready[0]."
actual_result: ready begins after the recommendation and SDK context evaluation treats recommended plus ready as the served ranking.
